{"title":"寝室","grey":true,"author":"Mr.Hope","time":"2020年9月1日","shareable":true,"content":[{"tag":"list","header":"寝室分布","content":[{"text":"本部校区本科寝室","icon":"/module/icon/locate.svg","base64Icon":"locate","path":"guide/dorm/locate/benbu"},{"text":"本部校区研究生寝室","icon":"/module/icon/locate.svg","base64Icon":"locate","path":"guide/dorm/locate/benbu-master"},{"text":"净月校区本科寝室","icon":"/module/icon/locate.svg","base64Icon":"locate","path":"guide/dorm/locate/jingyue"},{"text":"净月校区研究生寝室","icon":"/module/icon/locate.svg","base64Icon":"locate","path":"guide/dorm/locate/jingyue-master"}]},{"tag":"text","type":"p","heading":"寝室分配","text":["寝室的具体分配由辅导员全权负责，会在开学前分好。","分配寝室的主要原则为男女分寝和同专业同寝。另外大部分学院分配寝室的原则均为同地不同室，也就是说你的老乡不会成为你的室友。在满足条件的情况下，辅导员会完全随机分配(毕竟也都不认识你们)。","同地不同室的分配有助于寝室之间关系和睦，大家也能够更加了解并尊重其他地区同学的生活习惯，减少寝室之间因地域不同、生活习惯不同、做事风格不同等原因造成的冲突和对立的可能。"],"style":"text-indent: 1.5em; "},{"tag":"list","header":"寝室详细介绍","content":[{"text":"室内环境介绍","icon":"/module/icon/environment.svg","base64Icon":"environment","path":"guide/dorm/detail/env"},{"text":"个人区域介绍","icon":"/module/icon/environment.svg","base64Icon":"environment","path":"guide/dorm/detail/person"},{"text":"热水房","icon":"/module/icon/hot-water.svg","base64Icon":"hot-water","path":"guide/dorm/detail/hot-water"},{"text":"洗漱间","icon":"/module/icon/washing.svg","base64Icon":"washing","path":"guide/dorm/detail/washing"},{"text":"电梯","icon":"/module/icon/lift.svg","base64Icon":"lift","path":"guide/dorm/detail/lift"},{"text":"自习室","icon":"/module/icon/study.svg","base64Icon":"study","path":"guide/dorm/detail/self-study"},{"text":"卫生间","icon":"/module/icon/toilet.svg","base64Icon":"toilet","path":"guide/dorm/detail/toilet"},{"text":"洗衣机","icon":"/module/icon/washer.svg","base64Icon":"washer","path":"guide/dorm/detail/washer"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"寝室供电","content":[{"text":"供电时间","icon":"/module/icon/time.svg","base64Icon":"time","path":"guide/dorm/electricity/time"},{"text":"功率限制","icon":"/module/icon/power.svg","base64Icon":"power","path":"guide/dorm/electricity/power"},{"text":"缴纳电费","icon":"/module/icon/pay.svg","base64Icon":"pay","path":"guide/dorm/electricity/pay"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"寝室供网","content":[{"text":"寝室供网","icon":"/module/icon/network.svg","base64Icon":"network","path":"guide/dorm/network"}]},{"tag":"list","header":"规章制度","content":[{"text":"寝室门禁","icon":"/module/icon/door-guard.svg","base64Icon":"door-guard","path":"guide/dorm/door"},{"text":"走读与调宿","icon":"/module/icon/info.svg","base64Icon":"info","path":"guide/dorm/day-reading"},{"text":"违禁物品","icon":"/module/icon/ban.svg","base64Icon":"ban","path":"guide/dorm/ban"}]},{"tag":"list","content":[{"text":"Mr.Hope の建议","icon":"/module/icon/advice.svg","base64Icon":"advice","path":"guide/dorm/advice"}]}],"images":[],"id":"guide/dorm/index","scopeData":{"@type":"general","uniq_id":"guide/dorm/index","title":"寝室","digest":"寝室分配 寝室的具体分配由辅导员全权负责，会在开学前分好。 分配寝室的主要原则为男女分寝和同专业同寝。另外大部分学院分配寝室的原则均为同地不同室，也就是说你的老乡不会成为你的室友。在满足条件的情况下，辅导员会完全随机分配(毕竟也都不认识你们","thumbs":["https://mp.innenu.com/img/inNENU.jpg"],"tags":[]}}